---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Terms of Service — BoatHaven";
const description = "Read the BoatHaven Terms of Service.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-text mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none text-text-muted space-y-6">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> March 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing or using BoatHaven, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use the platform.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">2. Use of the Platform</h2>
      <p>BoatHaven provides a marketplace connecting boat owners with renters. We do not own, operate, or manage any boats listed on the platform. Users must be at least 18 years old to create an account.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">3. Bookings and Payments</h2>
      <p>All bookings are subject to owner approval unless marked as instant booking. Pricing is set by individual boat owners. BoatHaven is not responsible for disputes between owners and renters.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">4. User Responsibilities</h2>
      <p>Users are responsible for providing accurate information, maintaining account security, and complying with all applicable laws and regulations while using rented boats.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>BoatHaven is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for any damages arising from the use of the platform or any boat rental arranged through it.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">6. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the platform after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">7. Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about these terms, please <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
